{
  "chapter": 279,
  "chapter_summary": "项少龙在观星台与曹秋道决战后，利用智谋逃脱追杀。他利用肖月潭预先准备的滑雪板，在雪地上成功甩掉曹秋道，辗转逃往中牟。途中发现肖月潭留下的书信，得知十招之约竟是肖月潭虚张声势的计策，既惊且喜。抵达黄河岸边时，项少龙意外遇见滕翼、昌平君率领的秦军船队，纪嫣然、赵致等亲人也在船上，众人劫后重逢，悲喜交集。回到咸阳后，小盘亲自出城迎接，但项少龙感受到小盘已非昔日少年，城府日深，帝王心术渐显。在书斋密谈中，小盘透露已布下棋子监视嫪毐，并秘密调回王翦。当项少龙提及朱姬与嫪毐之事时，小盘对其生母的态度已变得冷酷无情，甚至直呼\"贱人\"。项少龙为朱姬辩护，与小盘产生分歧，深感应付小盘比对付吕不韦更加吃力。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_cao_qiu_dao",
      "speaker_name": "曹秋道",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "尔等何人？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 279,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_cao_qiu_dao",
      "text": "你中计了，看刀！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 279,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cao_qiu_dao",
      "speaker_name": "曹秋道",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "今趟看你走到哪里去？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 279,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_cao_qiu_dao",
      "text": "当然是回咸阳去，秋道小老儿我们后会无期！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 279,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_teng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "滕翼",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "少龙！少龙！是我们啊！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 279,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_teng_yi",
      "text": "现在我才明白什么叫恍如隔世，我曾想过永远再见不到你们。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 279,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "speaker_name": "纪嫣然",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我们曾想过自尽殉节，幸好接到消息，知你到了临淄，大家欢喜得发狂。嫣然和清姊遂不顾一切晋见储君，请他派人去齐国接你回来……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 279,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_ping_jun",
      "speaker_name": "昌平君",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "储君比任何人都紧张，立即要小弟抛下一切赶往临淄。只恨河水结冰，不过幸好如此，否则可能会互相错过，我们成了白走一趟。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 279,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_teng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "滕翼",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "荆家村虽有人来报讯，可是我们怎么等都见不到三弟回来，还以为三弟出事了。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 279,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "其他人好吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 279,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_ping_jun",
      "speaker_name": "昌平君",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我们与赵人达成和议，自中牟退兵，现在荆俊和桓齮仍在屯留。少龙此战既平定蒲鶮之乱，又大挫赵人锐气，功业盖世。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 279,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "功业若真能盖世，周良和这么多兄弟就不用客死异乡。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 279,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_teng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "滕翼",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "战争就是这样子，无论是胜是败，难免会有伤亡，三弟不必自责。唉！李牧确是个厉害人物。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 279,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_ping_jun",
      "speaker_name": "昌平君",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "吕不韦不是到了临淄吗？他当然不知你在那里吧！",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 279,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_chang_ping_jun",
      "text": "恰恰相反，我不单曾和他同席喝酒，还由他亲送我往稷下学宫与曹秋道决战。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 279,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "众人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "什么？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 279,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "赵致",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "柔姊怎会这样许身别人又不告知我们呢！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 279,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "speaker_name": "纪嫣然",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你没见到干爹吗？难道……",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 279,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "现在我只想好好睡一觉，更希望醒来时已身在咸阳。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 279,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "近日有什么大事发生？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 279,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_ping_jun",
      "speaker_name": "昌平君",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "韩王刚过世，由安太子继位，遣使向我们求和。储君着韩王安派韩非入秦，不知韩王安肯答应否？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 279,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_chang_ping_jun",
      "text": "储君一向欣赏韩非兄的治国理论，若韩非兄能在秦一展抱负，该是好事。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 279,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_ping_jun",
      "speaker_name": "昌平君",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "嫪毐更得太后宠幸，被封作长信侯后，俸禄与吕不韦相同，嚣张得令人难以忍受。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 279,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_jun",
      "speaker_name": "荆俊",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "今趟三哥无恙归来，必教一些人非常失望。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 279,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "赵致",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "夫君离家两年多！你绝想不到宝儿竟长得这么高大了。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 279,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "speaker_name": "纪嫣然",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "若不是为了宝儿，芳妹定会和我们同行，还害得小贞和小凤不能随行，她们为此哭了好几天。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 279,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_ping_jun",
      "speaker_name": "昌平君",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "这事见到储君再说。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 279,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "终于回家了！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 279,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_pan",
      "speaker_name": "小盘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "上将军辛苦了！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 279,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_pan",
      "speaker_name": "小盘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "上将军失踪的消息传回来后，家家户户为上将军求神许愿，希望上将军早日安全回来，现在终给他们盼到。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 279,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_pan",
      "text": "吕不韦尚未回来吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 279,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_pan",
      "speaker_name": "小盘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "他当然要赶在上将军之前回来，上将军在稷下学宫的一战确是精彩绝伦，为我大秦争得最大的光荣。你走后曹秋道亲向齐王请罪，承认无能把你留下。上将军知否齐王听到此事后，当日就气得病倒呢！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 279,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 338
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_pan",
      "text": "吕不韦回来了，那……唉！到宫内再说。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 279,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_pan",
      "speaker_name": "小盘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "一切都在寡人掌握之内，回去才说吧！",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 279,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_pan",
      "speaker_name": "小盘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "好大胆！这奸贼竟敢向外人泄出此事，万死不足辞其咎。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 279,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_pan",
      "text": "储君好像早知会有此事似的。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 279,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_pan",
      "speaker_name": "小盘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "别忘了寡人在嫪贼处布下茅焦这颗棋子，嫪贼的一举一动，怎瞒得过我。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 279,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_pan",
      "text": "储君自该早有对策。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 279,
      "line_start": 362,
      "line_end": 362
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_pan",
      "speaker_name": "小盘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "若在知情之后方派人去邯郸，便赶不及了。幸好多年前寡人早想到此点，已解决了这件事。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 279,
      "line_start": 364,
      "line_end": 366
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_pan",
      "text": "储君为何没有告诉我？",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 279,
      "line_start": 368,
      "line_end": 368
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_pan",
      "speaker_name": "小盘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "上将军当时远征外地，所以寡人一时忘了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 279,
      "line_start": 370,
      "line_end": 372
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_pan",
      "text": "储君怎样处置他们？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 279,
      "line_start": 374,
      "line_end": 374
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_pan",
      "speaker_name": "小盘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "当然是予他们足够的报酬，再把他们安置别地，教人找不到他们。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 279,
      "line_start": 376,
      "line_end": 378
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_pan",
      "speaker_name": "小盘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "师父不高兴吗？",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 279,
      "line_start": 384,
      "line_end": 384
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_pan",
      "text": "你变了很多。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 279,
      "line_start": 386,
      "line_end": 388
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_pan",
      "speaker_name": "小盘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我是不能不变，要坐稳这个位置，更是不能不变，但对上将军我则仍是那个小孩子。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 279,
      "line_start": 390,
      "line_end": 392
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_pan",
      "speaker_name": "小盘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "除上将军外，还有谁知道寡人的事呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 279,
      "line_start": 394,
      "line_end": 396
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_pan",
      "text": "除廷芳外，再没有第三个人知道此事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 279,
      "line_start": 400,
      "line_end": 400
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_pan",
      "speaker_name": "小盘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "好事不出门，恶事传千里，现在外面必是谣言满天飞，若让寡人知道有任何人提及此事，不理是谁，必杀无赦，还要抄家灭族，看谁再敢多言。哼！吕不韦、嫪毐！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 279,
      "line_start": 404,
      "line_end": 406
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_pan",
      "speaker_name": "小盘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "寡人已秘密把王翦调回来，两个月内返抵咸阳。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 279,
      "line_start": 410,
      "line_end": 412
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_pan",
      "text": "此事储君没请示太后吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 279,
      "line_start": 414,
      "line_end": 414
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_pan",
      "speaker_name": "小盘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "她既不把我当作儿子，我为何仍要看她的脸色做人。她在雍都更是肆无忌惮，与嫪毐的事弄到街知巷闻，天下谁不以此为笑柄，使我大秦蒙羞。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 279,
      "line_start": 416,
      "line_end": 420
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_pan",
      "text": "储君该记得曾经答应过我的事。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 279,
      "line_start": 422,
      "line_end": 424
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_pan",
      "speaker_name": "小盘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "到现在上将军仍要维护她吗？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 279,
      "line_start": 428,
      "line_end": 428
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_pan",
      "text": "是的！她总曾全心全意爱护你、扶持你，你亦曾把她视为生母。你若肯设身处地为她想想，该知她这么做对她没有半分好处，她仍然去做也只是人之常情。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 279,
      "line_start": 430,
      "line_end": 434
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_pan",
      "speaker_name": "小盘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "这里大部分报告都或多或少与郑国渠有关，最近寡人收到消息，郑国可能是韩王派来的人，上将军对此有何看法？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 279,
      "line_start": 436,
      "line_end": 438
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_pan",
      "text": "臣下累了，想回家休息。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 279,
      "line_start": 440,
      "line_end": 442
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_pan",
      "speaker_name": "小盘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "太傅动气了！很多事我都不想这么做的，但却知不这么做是不成的。太傅亦好应设身处地为寡人想想。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 279,
      "line_start": 444,
      "line_end": 448
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_pan",
      "text": "储君今年七月正式加冕为王，那时大权集于一身，太后还对储君有何影响力呢？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 279,
      "line_start": 450,
      "line_end": 452
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_pan",
      "speaker_name": "小盘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "上将军可知那贱人将印玺交给嫪毐随意使用，使寡人每晚睡难安寝？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 279,
      "line_start": 454,
      "line_end": 456
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_pan",
      "speaker_name": "小盘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "这贱人为嫪毐生下两个贼种，一个叫嫪政，一个叫嫪龙，上将军说这是什么意思？若非嫪贼与吕不韦勾结在一起，牵连太大，寡人忍不到七月就要将他碎尸万段。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 279,
      "line_start": 462,
      "line_end": 468
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_pan",
      "speaker_name": "小盘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "上将军可知嫪毐以假父自居，还说我这假子时日无多，他日将由他这假父加冕。哈！这蠢材瞪大眼睛都可做梦，寡人倒要看他怎样收场。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 279,
      "line_start": 470,
      "line_end": 474
    }
  ],
